[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0589","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0357","title":"Microsoft Windows 98 畸形 oshare 数据包远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 98 等操作系统在处理特制的 \"oshare\" 数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含无效分片偏移量的恶意网络数据包，触发系统资源耗尽或崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 98 及可能存在类似问题的其他操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0357"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.350","remediation":"Windows 98 已终止支持，无官方补丁。建议在网络边界防火墙或路由器上过滤入站异常分片报文（drop invalid fragments），阻止恶意「oshare」数据包到达目标主机。若业务允许，应尽快升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）并安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0357.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0587","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0821","title":"FreeBSD Seyon 2.1 本地溢出漏洞","description":"Seyon 终端模拟器 2.1 版本中存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于程序未对 -emulator 参数传入的程序路径进行有效验证，本地攻击者可指定恶意程序作为终端模拟器执行，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 及 RedHat Linux 4.0/5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，需拥有本地访问权限方能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0821"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.710","remediation":"移除 seyon 二进制文件的 setuid/setgid 权限：`chmod 755 $(which seyon)`，消除本地用户以特权启动任意程序的攻击面。建议彻底卸载 seyon（`apt-get remove seyon` 或 `pkg_delete seyon`），改用现代终端通信软件如 minicom 或 picocom。对于仍须使用的遗留系统，限制 seyon 可执行文件的属组并通过文件系统 ACL 控制访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/838","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/252"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0586","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0586.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0355","title":"CA ControlIT 4.5 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CA ControlIT 4.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地或远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的 ControlIT 服务发送特制请求，导致目标系统强制重启或强制已有用户会话注销，造成服务不可用。该漏洞影响 CA ControlIT 4.5 版本，攻击者可通过网络远程触发，无需复杂前置条件即可实现拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0355"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.103","remediation":"CA ControlIT 4.5 已停止维护，建议迁移至厂商当前支持的远程管理解决方案。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 ControlIT 服务端口（默认 TCP 1499），并禁用不必要的远程控制功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0355","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0355","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0355.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jqgq-vf46-2wc2/GHSA-jqgq-vf46-2wc2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82468/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000419.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--86340522-28cc-4ec8-9d76-b049bcd8b6d2.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0586.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0585","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0353","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":10799}}","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 rpc.pcnfsd 服务存在权限配置错误漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过修改主打印机假脱机目录的权限，获取远程 root 权限访问。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过篡改打印机假脱机目录权限实现权限提升至 root 权限，严重威胁系统安全。建议升级至修复版本或禁用 rpc.pcnfsd 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0353"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.860","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 到最新的Patched-Up 11.11 或更高版本，并应用最新的安全补丁包。具体步骤：1. 执行\"swinstall -s /somepath/hpus11v1_patch\"安装补丁；2. 检查并删除不必要的rpc.pcnfsd服务，使其处于禁用状态；3. 在防火墙上配置规则，仅允许本地网络段访问rpc.pcnfsd端口；4. 验证/spool目录的权限，确保持有者为root且权限为755，禁止其他用户修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-026.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9902-091","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0353","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0353.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/hpux_PHCO_14625.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHKL_15689.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x6000/5377/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0584","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0352","title":"ControlIT（又名 Remotely Possible）弱密码加密漏洞","description":"ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本（又名 Remotely Possible）存在弱密码加密漏洞，其加密算法强度不足，导致存储在系统配置中的凭据可被轻易破解。远程攻击者若能够访问受影响系统的配置文件或通过网络嗅探获取加密后的密码，可通过逆向分析加密算法还原明文凭据，进而获取系统控制权。该漏洞影响 ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0352"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 ControlIT 至 4.5 以上版本（若厂商已停止支持，应迁移至 Symantec pcAnywhere 或当前仍在维护的远程控制方案）。同时启用强密码策略，避免使用短于 8 位的密码，并限制远程访问来源 IP 以减少爆破风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0352"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0583","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0351","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 PASV 模式拒绝服务与未授权数据访问漏洞","description":"FTP 协议 PASV 被动模式存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可利用竞争条件在合法客户端之前连接至服务器为该客户端开放的临时数据端口，导致未经授权的数据访问和敏感信息窃取。若攻击者抢先占用该数据端口，还可导致合法客户端无法完成数据传输，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多种 FTP 服务器实现，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0351"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.610","remediation":"升级至支持 PASV 地址绑定检查的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 3.0+、ProFTPD 1.3.5+），配置数据端口仅接受与控制连接相同 IP 的连接请求。启用 FTPS（FTP over TLS/SSL，RFC 2228）加密数据通道防止窃听；条件允许时切换到 SFTP/SCP。在服务器上限制 PASV 端口范围为固定区间，并通过防火墙仅允许预期客户端 IP 访问该端口段作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://attrition.org/security/advisory/misc/infowar/iw_sec_01.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3389","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4.json","https://github.com/CWE-CAPEC/REST-API-wg/blob/5a8974308ef38e8ee4979e4a29b3b3a22c647822/json_repo/W/421.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82479/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000509.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0582","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0582.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0820","title":"FreeBSD Seyon PATH环境变量本地权限提升漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统下 Seyon 2.14b 版本存在相对路径处理不当漏洞。当 Seyon 执行 xterm 和 seyon-emu 命令时，未指定绝对路径而是依赖 PATH 环境变量查找可执行文件。本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 环境变量，在其中植入恶意的 xterm 或 seyon-emu 程序，诱导 Seyon 以用户权限执行恶意代码，从而实现权限提升。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限方可利用，且 Seyon 进程所运行的 shell 必须来源于 setuid 环境。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0820"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.583","remediation":"建议立即升级 seyon 至已修复该路径遍历问题的版本（参考 FreeBSD-SA-99:07 安全公告）。通过绝对路径调用 xterm 和 seyon-emu 命令，避免依赖 PATH 环境变量。如无法升级，可移除 seyon 二进制文件的 setuid 权限位（`chmod u-s /usr/local/bin/seyon`）或直接卸载该软件，改用 modem-manager 等替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/5996","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/838","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19609"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0582.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0581","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0581.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0819","title":"NTMail DeskPro 1.1 多个SQL注入漏洞","description":"NTMail 邮件服务器存在安全配置缺陷，即使管理员已明确在配置中禁用 VRFY 命令，该命令仍然可被远程攻击者使用。攻击者可通过 VRFY 命令枚举目标服务器上的有效邮箱账户，获取用户列表信息，为后续的社会工程学攻击或针对性钓鱼攻击提供攻击面。该漏洞影响 NTMail 邮件服务器软件，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0819"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.460","remediation":"升级至 Gordano 官方发布的修复版本（v5.01.0003 之后版本）；如无法升级，在防火墙或 SMTP 代理层过滤入站 VRFY 命令请求；或在 SMTP 服务器前置部署 ACL 规则限制仅允许可信 IP 发起 SMTP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94398141118586&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23264"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0581.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0580","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0818","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 kcms_configure NETPATH 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 kcms_configure 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 NETPATH 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致权限提升，获取 root 级别系统控制权。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需要本地 shell 权限即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0818"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.333","remediation":"从 Sun（甲骨文）获取并安装 Solaris 7 对应补丁（如 Patch ID 107081-xx 等 kcms_configure 相关补丁集）；若无法打补丁，立即移除 kcms_configure 的 setuid root 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/kcms_configure），该操作可阻断本地提权利用，或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本以彻底修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/831","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38433B7F5A.53F4SHADOWPENGUIN%40fox.nightland.net","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19647"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0579","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0815","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP Agent 内存泄漏拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP 服务代理存在内存泄漏漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统 SNMP 服务发送大量查询请求，导致系统内存资源被持续消耗直至耗尽，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP5 之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。安装 SP5 及以上版本补丁可修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0815"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.917","remediation":"升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，SP5 已修复 SNMP Agent 的内存泄漏问题。对于无法升级的系统，可在防火墙规则中限制对 UDP 端口 161 的访问，仅允许受信任的管理站发起 SNMP 查询，以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q196/2/70.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1974","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A952"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0578","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0350","title":"Rational Software ClearCase db_loader 竞态条件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Rational Software ClearCase for Unix 3.2 中的 db_loader 程序存在竞争条件漏洞。本地用户可利用该程序在处理 SUID 位时的竞态缺陷，通过精心构造的时序攻击绕过权限检查，将普通文件权限提升至 root 级别。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限并精确控制竞争窗口，成功利用后可获取目标系统的完全控制权，CVSS 评分 6.2，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0350"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.480","remediation":"升级 Rational ClearCase 至 3.2.1 及以上版本，官方已修复 db_loader 中的竞态条件问题。如无法升级，可手动移除 db_loader 程序的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /path/to/db_loader），并限制仅授权用户可执行该程序，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0350","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19429"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0577","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0813","title":"Cfingerd ALLOW_EXECUTION 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cfingerd（finger协议守护进程实现）存在特权管理不当漏洞。当启用 ALLOW_EXECUTION 选项时，系统未能在代表用户执行程序前正确丢弃 root 权限，导致本地攻击者可通过请求服务执行任意程序来获取 root 权限，进而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响运行 Cfingerd 的各类 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0813"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.607","remediation":"立即升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.0 或更高版本（当前最新为 1.4.3），该版本已修复执行外部程序时未正确丢弃 root 权限的安全缺陷。如无法升级，在 cfingerd.conf 中将 ALLOW_EXECUTION 设置为 false 以禁用该功能，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0813"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0576","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0812","title":"Samba smbmnt 本地文件系统挂载竞争条件漏洞","description":"Samba 组件中的 smbmnt 工具存在竞态条件漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用文件系统挂载过程中的时间窗口，在任意目录挂载文件系统，导致权限提升或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Samba 多个版本，需要本地用户权限作为攻击条件，CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0812"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-07-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.467","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 smbmnt/smbmount 中的条件竞争漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 smbmnt 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/smbmnt），仅允许受信任用户执行，通过文件系统权限限制本地普通用户对 smbmnt 的访问以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0812"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0575","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0811","title":"Samba smbd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 之前版本的 smbd 守护进程在处理畸形消息命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向目标 Samba 服务发送特制的恶意消息包触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或实现本地权限提升，获取系统高权限。该漏洞影响所有 Samba 2.0.5 之前版本，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0811"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.360","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 smbd 进程处理畸形消息命令时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 smb.conf 中限制可访问 smbd 的源 IP 地址范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19428"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator Cookie 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本存在安全绕过漏洞。当用户启用 JavaScript 且已选择\"仅接受来自正浏览页面同一服务器之 Cookie\"选项时，浏览器仍不会对 Cookie 设置行为发出警告。攻击者可利用恶意网页绕过 Cookie 同源策略，跨站设置或窃取用户 Cookie，导致用户隐私泄露或会话劫持。漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"停止使用 Netscape Communicator 4.x，升级至 Mozilla Firefox 或其它现代浏览器，并在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。对于仍必须使用 Netscape 的场景，可在浏览器首选项中关闭 JavaScript 功能（Edit → Preferences → Advanced → Scripts & Plugins → 取消启用 JavaScript）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"}]